Introduction

GBB (an acronym for Gawi Bawi Boo; in English Rock Paper Scissors) was a five-member girl group under ProBeat Company. They debuted on May 1, 2018 with the mini-album "Girls Be The Best".

On March 20, 2020, Chaehee confirmed through an Instagram live on her personal account that GBB had disbanded.
